### [The Goal - Eliyahu Goldratt](https://www.amazon.com/Goal-Process-Ongoing-Improvement/dp/0884271951)

<% link_to "https://www.amazon.com/Goal-Process-Ongoing-Improvement/dp/0884271951", :class => 'img-link' do %>
